AdGuard Home is a network-wide DNS server that blocks ads and trackers.
This plugin integrates AdGuard Home into OPNsense and adds a
"Services -> AdGuard Home" page to enable/disable the service and manage
its runtime options.

AdGuard Home owns its own configuration (AdGuardHome.yaml) and rewrites it
whenever you change settings in its web interface, so all filtering, DNS
and blocklist configuration is done from AdGuard Home's own admin UI. This
plugin manages the service (rc.conf) and links out to that UI.

WWW: https://adguard.com/en/adguard-home/overview.html
